    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014it's been babied in a heated garage and looks like it just rolled off the lot! Not a scratch or a dent to be found, and the interior still smells brand new. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
