      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, this car is an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows\u2014it\u2019s in pristine, showroom-ready condition! It drives so smoothly and looks just as good as the day it was first driven off the lot. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
