      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine, showing factory-spec compression across all rotor faces. The intricate vacuum-controlled boost system has been meticulously preserved, ensuring a linear power band and the characteristic 10-8-10 psi boost pattern. The chassis retains its original structural integrity, complemented by a four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in original Montego Blue with zero clear-coat failure, the interior is equally pristine, featuring high-bolster seats with no leather fatigue or sun-damaged plastics. This is a collector-grade unit for the purist who demands mechanical transparency and peak OEM performance.",
